REQUIREMENTS:
I want to be able to have accounts with a balance:
    - Day to day account with $1000, for example;
    - Saving's account with $5000, for example;

I want to be able to register expenditures.
    - Register a transaction;
        - e.g. I have spent $X from Day-To-Day account;
    - I want to be able to see a history of my transactions;


Account
